---
---
<section class="faq-section">
  <div class="faq-container">
    <div class="faq-header">
      <p class="faq-subtitle">QUESTIONS, ANSWERED</p>
      <h2 class="faq-title">Frequently asked questions</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq-item" open>
        <summary class="faq-summary">
          <span class="faq-question">Can I start with just a fence now and add a matching gate later?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon"></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
          <p>Absolutely. Because we custom-manufacture everything in our local factory and keep your property's specifications on file, we can easily fabricate and install a perfectly matching gate or additional fencing in the future.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
      
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-summary">
          <span class="faq-question">Do you manufacture and install everything in-house?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon"></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
          <p>Yes. Unlike competitors who sub-contract installation or buy pre-fabricated panels, Mulholland designs, manufactures, and installs everything. This ensures complete quality control, a cohesive and unified look, and a single point of accountability.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-summary">
          <span class="faq-question">How does aluminum compare to wood or steel?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon"></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
          <p>Our powder-coated 6063 aircraft-grade aluminum is infinitely superior for coastal and sunny climates. It will never rust like steel or wrought iron, and will never rot, warp, or require staining like wood. It's completely maintenance-free.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-summary">
          <span class="faq-question">Can you automate my gate?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon"></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-content">
          <p>Yes. We specialize in smart automation. We can integrate whisper-quiet motors, remote keypads, and smartphone apps (like Ring or Nest) directly into your custom gate design.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
 .faq-section {
 width: 100%;
 background-color: #ffffff;
 padding: 93px 20px 100px 20px;
 display: flex;
 justify-content: center;
 }

 .faq-container {
 width: 100%;
 max-width: 695px; /* Divider line width requested */
 display: flex;
 flex-direction: column;
 }

 .faq-header {
 text-align: center;
 margin-bottom: 50px;
 }
 
 .faq-subtitle {
 font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
 font-weight: 600; /* Bold */
 font-size: 12px;
 line-height: 16px;
 letter-spacing: 2.64px;
 color: #2C65B0;
 text-transform: uppercase;
 margin: 0 0 15px 0;
 }

 .faq-title {
 font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
 font-weight: 800; /* Bold */
 font-size: 45px;
 line-height: 45px;
 letter-spacing: -0.94px;
 color: #14110E;
 margin: 0;
 }

 .faq-list {
 display: flex;
 flex-direction: column;
 }

 .faq-item {
 border-bottom: 1px solid #2C65B0;
 overflow: hidden;
 }

 /* No border bottom on the last item to match typical design unless requested, wait screenshot has border? I will leave border-bottom on all except last */
 .faq-item:last-child {
 border-bottom: none;
 }

 .faq-summary {
 display: flex;
 justify-content: space-between;
 align-items: center;
 padding: 30px 0;
 cursor: pointer;
 list-style: none; /* Remove default triangle */
 }

 .faq-summary::-webkit-details-marker {
 display: none; /* Safari */
 }

 .faq-question {
 font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
 font-weight: 800; /* Bold */
 font-size: 18px;
 line-height: 28px;
 color: #14110E;
 max-width: 90%;
 }

 .faq-icon {
 width: 24px;
 height: 24px;
 background-image: url('/gates-and-fences/assets/images/faq/+.svg');
 background-size: contain;
 background-repeat: no-repeat;
 background-position: center;
 flex-shrink: 0;
 transition: transform 0.3s ease;
 }

 /* When details is open, change icon */
 .faq-item[open] .faq-icon {
 background-image: url('/gates-and-fences/assets/images/faq/-.svg');
 }

 .faq-content {
 padding-bottom: 30px;
 animation: slideDown 0.3s ease-out;
 }

 .faq-content p {
 font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
 font-weight: 400; /* Regular */
 font-size: 16px;
 line-height: 26px;
 color: #635C57;
 margin: 0;
 }

 @keyframes slideDown {
 from {
 opacity: 0;
 transform: translateY(-10px);
 }
 to {
 opacity: 1;
 transform: translateY(0);
 }
 }

 /* ─── RESPONSIVE ───────────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .faq-section {
  padding: 34px 20px 60px 20px !important;
  }

  .faq-header {
  margin-bottom: 35px !important;
  }

  .faq-title {
  font-size: 24px !important;
  line-height: 27px !important;
  letter-spacing: -0.9px !important;
  }

  .faq-summary {
  min-height: 72px !important;
  padding: 10px 0 !important;
  }
  
  .faq-question {
  font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif !important;
  font-weight: 800 !important;
  font-size: 18px !important;
  line-height: 26px !important;
  color: #14110E !important;
  }

  .faq-content p {
  font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif !important;
  font-weight: 400 !important;
  font-size: 16px !important;
  line-height: 26px !important;
  color: #635C57 !important;
  }
  }
</style>
